trans-unit.source: Overwrite selections row by row. Empty row doesn't overwrite the selection. Additional rows are possible.
Name a Location without Address. !It overwrites a set "Location"!
Campaigns normally hide if there's no upcoming Event - here you can overwrite that setting. It will be listet as long as "openend" is set or there's an upcoming Event.
You can overwrite the Contacts of the assigned Client. The priority of Contacts is 1. Campaign - 2. Client
Set the date when the Campaign should be listet in the Client's Archive. Please be aware that the Client's archive has to be activated in the Client's record, otherwise there's no effect on the date!
You can overwrite the Contacts of the assigned Campaigns and Client. The priority of Contacts is 1. News - 2. Campaign (ONLY if just one is assigned) - 3. Client
Change Invitation Report Stop Time. Default is 24 Hours. It's possible to add and sub Hours.
Default: 2 Weeks before Event date -> fixed on Friday of this week
Change Invitation Report Stop Time. Default is 24 Hours. It's possible to add and sub Hours.
